  python demo_rollback_scenarios.py

  # Use the convenient batch runner
  run_pbix_tests.bat SCRPA_Time_v2.pbix

  🔄 Rollback Process Flow:

  1. Create Backup → 2. Validate Input → 3. Update Parameter
                                             ↓ (on success)
  6. Cleanup ← 5. Validate Output ← 4. Create Output File
       ↑                                     ↓ (on failure)
       └── Rollback from Backup ←──────────────┘

